## Technical Stack

| Category | Tools |
|----------|-------|
| Language | Python 3 |
| Data Manipulation | pandas, NumPy |
| Modeling | scikit-learn (Logistic Regression, Random Forest), XGBoost |
| Imbalanced Data | class_weight, SMOTE (imbalanced-learn) |
| Explainability | SHAP (global + local) |
| Evaluation | Precision, Recall, F1-score, PR-AUC |
| Visualization | matplotlib, seaborn |
| Environment | Jupyter Notebook |

