## How to Run
```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/SanjayKajeepeta/Explainable-Fraud-Detection.git
cd Explainable-Fraud-Detection

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Launch notebooks
jupyter notebook notebooks/01_data_exploration.ipynb
```

**Dataset:** This project uses the 
[Credit Card Fraud Detection dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud) 
from Kaggle (ULB Machine Learning Group). Download `creditcard.csv` and 
place it in a `data/` folder before running.

